params.1319:
The Corrupted Hunllef is the boss located within The Corrupted Gauntlet, an activity within the elven capital city of Prifddinas.

Access to The Corrupted Gauntlet is unlocked by completing The Gauntlet.

Attack Styles - Ranged, Magic, Special
Immunities - Poison, Venom
Slayer categories - None
params.1320:
Mandatory requirements:
- Song of the Elves
- Access to The Corrupted Gauntlet

Combat Achievement task difficulty:
- Elite
- Master
- Grandmaster
